          }
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Planning Node Set First Wave\n\nShip a concrete v1 planning schema instead of continuing abstract node-set debate.\n\nFirst wave node types:\n- `goal`\n- `task`\n- `decision`\n- `open-question`\n- `constraint`\n\nModeling rule:\n- `dependency` is edge-first in v1\n- planning nodes stay static and fragment-safe\n- prompt extraction should treat these as the canonical planning surface",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": true,
        "root": true,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
