      "width": 390,
      "height": 300,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Ship In V1\n\nImplement these node types now:\n\n- `goal`\n- `task`\n- `decision`\n- `open-question`\n- `constraint`\n\nWhy these first:\n- highest planning value\n- low semantic overlap\n- useful in prompts and summaries\n- can be rendered as mostly static nodes\n- survive fragment traversal cleanly",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
