      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Defer In V1\n\nDo not make these first-class planning nodes yet:\n\n- `dependency`\n- `acceptance-criteria`\n- `risk-edge-case`\n\nReason:\n- more structurally ambiguous\n- likely partly relational rather than purely node-shaped\n- better informed after first-wave authoring feedback",
