    {
      "id": "nodeset-first-wave-dependency",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Dependency Rule",
      "position": {
        "x": 380,
        "y": 250
      },
      "width": 390,
      "height": 240,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Dependency Rule\n\n`dependency` is edge-first in v1.\n\nUse dependency edges with metadata like:\n- `kind`\n- `hard`\n- `external`\n- `status`\n\nIf a prerequisite must be modeled as an object, represent that object as a normal node and connect it with dependency edges.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
        "_classBinding": {
          "key": "markdown",
          "sourceRef": "github://twilite-zone/public/library/classes/nodes/markdown.node-class.node",
