      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Canonical Fields\n\n`goal`\n- `summary`\n- `horizon`\n- `priority`\n- `status`\n\n`task`\n- `summary`\n- `status`\n- `owner`\n- `priority`\n- `estimate`\n\n`decision`\n- `summary`\n- `status`\n- `rationale`\n- `supersedes`\n\n`open-question`\n- `summary`\n- `status`\n- `owner`\n- `resolutionTarget`\n\n`constraint`\n- `summary`\n- `kind`\n- `scope`\n- `hardness`",
        "memo": "",
