    {
      "id": "nodeset-first-wave-implementation",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Implementation Punch List",
      "position": {
        "x": 820,
        "y": 740
      },
      "width": 470,
      "height": 320,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Implementation Punch List\n\n1. Define schema for the five first-wave node types.\n2. Register them in the node-type/dictionary system.\n3. Give each a simple authored view with distinct compact styling.\n4. Keep `dependency` edge-first.\n5. Update prompt/context extraction to pull:\n   - active goals\n   - open tasks\n   - settled decisions\n   - unresolved questions\n   - binding constraints\n6. Reassess deferred node types after real planning-graph usage.",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false,
