      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Current Library State\n\nThe planning-node library already contains class artifacts for:\n- `goal`\n- `task`\n- `decision`\n- `constraint`\n- `open-question`\n- `acceptance-criteria`\n- `risk`\n- `dependency`\n\nSo the first-wave task is not greenfield. The real work is to reconcile that broader library with the narrower approved first-wave contract.",
